{"tid":1092704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唐公嶺車房爆炸焚16車 最少5部逾百萬元古董車","createTime":"2019-04-05T05:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T15:34:14.000Z","uid":3090,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"15106ca970239bf5f70cb2f14ef44f969ec90fd2","tid":1092704,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ri4pSy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ri4pSy.png&h=d4cad26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBwJFqU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBwJFqU.png&h=96b131cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hSPvkqV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhSPvkqV.png&h=549d668a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odOLTLV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodOLTLV.png&h=b995b818&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/05/131001_cd07acb9101536041131f7f0f71c4191.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F131001_cd07acb9101536041131f7f0f71c4191.png&h=6caf17f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/05/131002_77e7f15d26ff51aee48aabb710630ae7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F131002_77e7f15d26ff51aee48aabb710630ae7.png&h=794eca52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/05/131003_421fa52f64cc3fd1fc66c148b1e4a529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F05%2F131003_421fa52f64cc3fd1fc66c148b1e4a529.png&h=87fb023f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【11:45】更新內容<br />\n<br />\n上水粉錦公路唐公嶺，凌晨1時許，一個面積7千呎的車房發生火警，火勢猛烈冒出濃煙，並傳出爆炸聲。消防員接報到場，開三條喉及出動三隊煙帽隊灌救，附近約20人疏散。有村民帶同寵物離開，一名老婦走火警時擦傷右腳，現場敷治拒絕送院。<br />\n<br />\n消防員約兩小時後將火救熄，起火車房沒有人留守。現場所見，大約有16部車及兩個貨櫃焚毀，當中最少5架是古董車，消防調查懷疑電線短路引起火警，事件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，焚毀的古董車是車房東主私人珍藏，包括有Essex Motors開篷車和Humber Vogue等，分別是30年代及60年代的產品，要在粵語長片才能見到，估計總值過百萬元。"},{"pid":"04058ea5e8d1f9a7e2873d531471b8f23e3996ab","tid":1092704,"uid":70322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:15:37.000Z","msg":"正評是常識"},{"pid":"06d5bdda1a6d40ffaf21c68b416032683671b82c","tid":1092704,"uid":144,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"仇富撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90128d96140a21770895acc58868f2478e7d19c3","tid":1092704,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唐公嶺入面個戶定門口上山個邊"},{"pid":"e2d32ee0ee3d2d5e9c5dd36695e559303a3b8099","tid":1092704,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"我大概知邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d990bd3c0a576dda86e17befa0d249353311796","tid":1092704,"uid":135503,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"清明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先人想揸返走d古董車"},{"pid":"338e74d23f434e143a4da9aa7f5b71a93a805198","tid":1092704,"uid":55386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"清明燒真車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26691bf2e74bd5ac1e62ba06e14b027888fb48bf","tid":1092704,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"內容令人愉悦"},{"pid":"a4273b7146f6140fb21347b4e07264c4cf20d145","tid":1092704,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"